  { q: 'What does FN mean on TikTok?', a: 'On TikTok, FN almost always means "F***ing" as an intensifier — for example "fn hilarious" means "f***ing hilarious." It is used for strong emphasis.' },
  { q: 'Does FN mean Fortnite?', a: 'Yes, in gaming contexts FN is a common abbreviation for Fortnite. If the conversation is about gaming, that is almost certainly what it means.' },
  { q: 'Is FN the same as FYN?', a: 'No. FYN means "Fine" or "For Your Note." FN as an expletive is a separate abbreviation entirely.' },
